column8: DAP rep demands state gov't reveal details on Lebuhraya Peel land sale, hospital projectGEORGE TOWN: A DAP lawmaker has called on the state government to divulge more details on the controversial Lebuhraya Peel land sale and hospital expansion project.Yap Soo Huey (DAP - Pulau Tikus) said the state government should disclose details about the land deal and the hospital expansion project so that the public can be better informed.She also said that as part of the deal, there should also be an agreement to make it compulsory for the hospital management to set up a fund to help the locals.https://sg.news.yahoo.com/dap-rep-demands-s...-144258869.htmlAt least she is thinking about the rakyat, good for her i like
